/>\n執業大律師陸偉雄指，夾公仔店必須領足4個牌照方可合法經營，包括商業登記、有獎娛樂遊戲牌照、公眾娛樂場所牌照及相關消防牌照，若被發現未申領牌照，經營者可能觸犯《賭博條例》，最高可罰款5萬港元及監禁2年。而即使領取所有牌照，仍需遵循牌照條款，<span style=\"color: red;\">包括就每個中獎機會而付出的款項不多於5港元，獎品不多於300港元，亦不得使用現金等，違規者可遭吊銷牌照。</span><br />\n<br />\n仲有邊款夾公仔係唔超過$5<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c56bbe6dcf22a0420d68bc084c9bf4f31b765df","tid":1144076,"uid":32577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"793c9fb75a5b67bab792442d33d9917cdf674a77","tid":1144076,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T01:40:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8E%A2%E5%B0%84%E7%87%88%EF%BC%9A%E5%A4%BE%E5%85%AC%E4%BB%94%E5%BA%97%E7%8D%8E%E5%93%81%E3%80%80%E9%80%BE300%E5%8D%B3%E9%81%95%E8%A6%8F-002225120.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%258E%25A2%25E5%25B0%2584%25E7%2587%2588%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%25A4%25BE%25E5%2585%25AC%25E4%25BB%2594%25E5%25BA%2597%25E7%258D%258E%25E5%2593%2581%25E3%2580%2580%25E9%2580%25BE300%25E5%258D%25B3%25E9%2581%2595%25E8%25A6%258F-002225120.html&d=6Mci4xO0oquEcg2hov7%2Fcife5Xzx4ME6JwL9AZsFK0I%3D&h=54254aef\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8E%A2%E5%B0%84%E7%87%88%EF%BC%9A%E5%A4%BE%E5%85%AC%E4%BB%94%E5%BA%97%E7%8D%8E%E5%93%81%E3%80%80%E9%80%BE300%E5%8D%B3%E9%81%95%E8%A6%8F-002225120.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/X6OAujfItVLOD8mSPsFkvw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDA1/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/28ba23023543896aa4387bb24402db6d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FX6OAujfItVLOD8mSPsFkvw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDA1%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F28ba23023543896aa4387bb24402db6d&h=5e763e7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開設夾公仔機店必須取得4種牌照，曾有商場的小店被指無牌經營而被勒令停業。<br />\n<br />\n遊戲機中心的掟彩虹及夾公仔機深受老幼歡迎，愈來愈多無人看舖的夾公仔機小店開設